title: Lucky Farm 1.3.1
description:
Operating system:
Windows XP/Vista/7/8 

Description:
Match cards before the timer runs out and don't waste to many remaining turns. This game is a great way to test your kid memory speed and recall limits as they have fun matching cows, pigs, and other animals in 20 levels that change each time the game is played. It also fun as an adult to see if you can beat a kids game. Level 20 is not easy!
